  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients with vitiligo vulgaris are treated with Pimecrolimus twice a day during 6 months.
      After a baseline visit, patient returns for a control visit after 3 and 6 months of
      treatment. One reference lesion is clinically evaluated with pictures.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
