  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Active or stable vitiligo vulgaris

          -  lesions at head or neck + maximum 10% lesions at the rest of the body

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Topica during last 2 weeks

          -  Photo(chemo)therapy during last 4 weeks

          -  Segmentary vitiligo
      </textblock>
